I than searched the New York mystery number and then it appeared as being somewhere in China named "Makit". I cant seem to find that location and I'm sorta weirded out. Now i am not saying my phone is bugged but I am a pretty big fan of internet privacy and cell phone privacy. I am also highly against most militarized police departments and have openly searched a lot of stuff in the past couple of years relating to content like that. I'm just wondering if my phone could be bugged or tapped for any reason because of my search history against the government/police departments. I'm not saying that is what this is but I am just sorta worried and I want some answers.
